rowspan=\"5\" | 2011\n|''[[One Life (2011 film)|One Life]]''\n|Narrator (voice)\n|[[Documentary film|Documentary]]\n|-\n|''[[Cowboys & Aliens]]''\n|Jake Lonergan\n|\n|-\n|''[[Dream House (2011 film)|Dream House]]''\n|Will Atenton / Peter Ward\n|\n|-\n|''[[The Adventures of Tintin (film)|The Adventures of Tintin]]''\n|[[Ivan Ivanovitch Sakharine]] / [[Red Rackham]] ([[motion capture]])\n|\n|-\n|''{{sortname|The|Girl with the Dragon Tattoo|dab=2011 film}}''\n|[[Mikael Blomkvist]]\n|\n|-\n|2012\n|''[[Skyfall]]''\n| rowspan=\"2\" | James Bond\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2015\n|''[[Spectre (2015 film)|Spectre]]''\n|Also co-producer\n|-\n| ''[[Star Wars: The Force Awakens]]''\n| [[Stormtrooper (Star Wars)|Stormtrooper]] FN-1824\n| [[Cameo appearance|Uncredited cameo]]<ref name=\"Craig-Storm Trooper\"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/pablohidalgo/status/749616406245699584|title=Yeah, same with Infinity| last=Hidalgo|first=Pablo|date=3 July 2016|website=@pablohidalgo|accessdate=7 July 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2017\n| ''[[Logan Lucky]]''\n| Joe Bang\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Kings (2017 film)|Kings]]''<ref name=\"Kings\">{{cite news| title=China's Bliss Media, Maven Pictures to Finance Halle Berry's L.A. Riots Movie| url=https://variety.com/2016/film/news/la-riots-movie-halle-berry-bliss-media-maven-pictures-1201943527/|accessdate=3 January 2017| work=Variety| date=16 December 2016}}</ref>\n| Obie Hardison\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Knives Out]]''\n| Detective Benoit Blanc\n|\n|-\n| 2020\n| style=\"background:#ffc;\"|''[[No Time to Die]]'' {{dagger}}\n| James Bond\n| Post-production\n|-\n|}\n\n===Television===\n<!-- Please note: do NOT use \"rowspans\" per WP:FILMOGRAPHY -->\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\"|Notes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"7\" | 1993\n|''[[Zorro (1990 TV series)|Zorro]]''\n|Lieutenant Hidalgo\n|2 episodes\n|-\n|''[[Drop the Dead Donkey]]''\n|Fixx\n|Episode: \"George and His Daughter\"\n|-\n|''{{sortname|The|Young 