} ||[[Westpac Stadium]], [[Wellington]] ||1 March 2015\n|-\n| colspan=\"5\" |<small>Last updated: 14 July 2019</small><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/stats/index.html?batting_fielding_first=2;class=2;filter=advanced;result=1;template=results;trophy=12;type=team;view=innings|title=Team records {{!}} One-Day Internationals {{!}} Cricinfo Statsguru {{!}} ESPNcricinfo.com|website=Cricinfo|access-date=11 June 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150220004356/http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/stats/index.html?batting_fielding_first=2;class=2;filter=advanced;result=1;template=results;trophy=12;type=team;view=innings|archive-date=20 February 2015|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|}\nNote : In the [[2011 Cricket World Cup]], England scored 338\u20138 in the second innings to tie their game against India.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.espncricinfo.com/series/8039/report/433568/india-vs-england-11th-match-group-b-icc-cricket-world-cup-2010-11|title=Recent Match Report \u2013 India vs England, World Cup, 11th Match, Group B {{!}} ESPNcricinfo.com|website=ESPNcricinfo|language=en|access-date=2019-06-18}}</ref>\n\n===Won tournament===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"3\" | 100% win record<ref name=matches>{{cite web | url = http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/stats/index.html?class=2;filter=advanced;orderby=win_loss_ratio;template=results;trophy=12;type=team;view=series | publisher = Cricinfo | accessdate = 24 March 2015 | title = Statistics \u2013 Statsguru \u2013 World Cup \u2013 Team records | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150813050256/http://stats.espncricinfo.com/ci/engine/stats/index.html?class=2;filter=advanced;orderby=win_loss_ratio;template=results;trophy=12;type=team;view=series | archive-date = 13 August 2015 | url-status = live }}</ref>\n|-\n! Team || Year || Matches played\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{cr|Australia}} || ([[2007 Cricket World Cup|2007]]) || 11\n|-\n|align=\"left\"|{{cr|