k blue T-shirt facing to the right.  He is wearing a wide-brimmed white hat and is standing in front of some empty bleachers with trees further behind.]]\n[[File:Ricky Ponting YM.jpg|right|thumb|Australian [[Ricky Ponting]] scored more than 1700 runs and has the most appearances (46) and most matches as captain (29) in World Cups.|alt=A white man with stubble, wearing a dark blue baseball cap with three white stripes on the peak and a yellow logo on the front.  He is wearing a dark blue top with three yellow stripes down each arm from the shoulder and is leaning forward in front of a doorway.]]\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!| Record\n! colspan=\"2\" | First\n! colspan=\"2\" | Second\n!| Ref(s)\n|-\n|Fastest double century\n|{{cricon|West Indies}} [[Chris Gayle]] v [[Zimbabwe cricket team|Zimbabwe]] ([[2015 Cricket World Cup|2015]])\n|138 balls\n|{{flagicon|New Zealand}} [[Martin Guptill]] v [[West Indies cricket team|West Indies]] ([[2015 Cricket World Cup|2015]])\n|152 balls\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.espncricinfo.com/icc-cricket-world-cup-2015/content/story/837817.html|title = Highest WC score, fastest double-ton, record sixes|date = 24 February 2015|publisher = Cricinfo|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150226161847/http://www.espncricinfo.com/icc-cricket-world-cup-2015/content/story/837817.html|archive-date = 26 February 2015|url-status = live}}</ref>\n|-\n|Fastest 150\n|{{cricon|RSA}} [[AB de Villiers]] v [[West Indies cricket team|West Indies]] ([[2015 Cricket World Cup|2015]])\n|64 balls\n| {{Flagicon|PAK}} [[Imran Nazir (cricketer)|Imran Nazir]] v [[Zimbabwe national cricket team|Zimbabwe]] ([[2007 Cricket World Cup|2007]])\n| 116 balls\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url = https://www.bbc.com/sport/0/cricket/31655996|title = AB De Villiers hits fastest ODI 150 in South Africa World Cup win|date = 27 February 2015|publisher = BBC Sport|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150924185422/http://www.bbc.com/sport/0/cricket/31655996|archive-date = 24 S